CA oak trees have specific requirements.  Area extending 6 ft. above trunk, leave uncovered & undisturbed.  Trim mature oaks in June/July.
Some places in USA are not zoned such as Houston, Texas.  Believe it or not.  : )

Zoning:
Earliest of land-use tools.
In CA all land must be zoned including Federal property or land under native American tribe control.
The precise structure and the organization of the General Plan (besides 7 mandatory elements) is left largely to the local jurisdiction.  💋🌲

General Plan, Seven Mandatory Elements:
1) Land use
2) Circulation
3) Conservation
4) Housing
5) Noise
6) Public safety 
7) Open space
Since 1971: Planning & Zoning requires cities or counties to have a General plan/ a constitution for land use.
California's Planning & Zoning Law: California's land is an  exhaustible resource and not just a commodity.  Lists actions to protect.

Police Power:
Government's authority to regulate the health, safety, welfare & morals of its citizens.
Escheat: Process were private property reverts to gov. if owner passes on with no heirs and no will.
Most property taxes are based on value and are known as ad valorem.
Taxation: The right of gov. to tax property owners to raise money for general purposes and special assessments.

Eminent Domain:
Power for Gov. to take private property for public use.  Appraisal usually required.  Owner has say in compensation amount.
